email subject: Thanks for applying to Stripe!
email body: Hi Aaryaman, Thanks so much for submitting your application for the Software Engineer, Intern role! As a reminder, we have recorded your location preference and cohort preference (if applicable, Winter, or Summer) based on your application responses so only one application is required. With the high volume of applications, our University Recruiting team will review applications on a rolling basis which may cause a delay in our response times. We appreciate your understanding and, in the meantime, encourage you to check out our quick guide to Stripe culture [0], our blog [1], and our LinkedIn page [2] to get a feel for what we're up to at Stripe. We hope to connect soon! Stripe [0] https://stripe.com/jobs/life-at-stripe [1] https://stripe.com/blog [2] https://www.linkedin.com/company/stripe ** Please note: this inbox does not accept replies so your warm responses will not be received

email subject: Aaryaman, Thanks for Applying for Salesforce's Summer 2025 Intern - Software Engineer
email body: Hi Aaryaman, Hooray! You have officially applied for the Summer 2025 Intern - Software Engineer opening at Salesforce. Thank you for letting us know you’re interested in discovering new opportunities with us. Good news – your information is now in the cloud. A member of our recruiting team will personally review your application. If you’re a potential match for one of our open positions, we’ll be in touch. If we don’t have the right role for you now, don’t worry, we’ll keep your information on file for future opportunities. You can check on the status of your application at any point by logging into our Careers Site. ( https://salesforce.wd12.myworkdayjobs.com/External_Career_Site) Click the button in the right corner, then select “view profile.” Thanks again for considering Salesforce and have a great week! The Salesforce Recruiting Team P.S. This is an auto-generated message. Please do not reply to this email. For information on Salesforce's commitment regarding your privacy, please see our Candidate Privacy Statement Get to know us better here: This email was intended for aaryaman04@gmail.com salesforce.com inc. • Salesforce Tower, 415 Mission Street, 3rd Floor, San Francisco, CA 94105
